      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;card&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;card-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;bubble-quote mb-4&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;quote-mark&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      We Are Still &lt;strong&gt;Setting Things Up&lt;/strong&gt; Expect Things To Be Wonky Till End Of Year-ish 2025.&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;quote-mark&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;card&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;card-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-megaplex&#34;&gt;The Megaplex&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Megalisp&amp;rsquo;s Community&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the Megaplex — the community hub for Megalisp.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re trying to cultivate Techno-Optimism through a Retro-Futurist Aesthetic.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Going all-in on Lisp via Racket; Hoping to take it and move it somewhere else ultimately.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;(We&amp;rsquo;ll see how possible that is in-practice lol)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;da-rules&#34;&gt;Da Rules&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;This Is A Christian Minecraft Server&amp;rdquo; level community. Keep it safe-for-work, safe-for-church.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
